The Game returns with his third and supposedly last CD LAX. Keisha Cole is 
featured on the lead off track &#039;Game&#039;s Pain.&#039; Other guests include Ice Cube, 
Raekwon, Ludacris, Bilal and Raheem DeVaughn, appearing on "State of 
Emergency," "Bulletproof Diaries," "Cali Sunshine" and "Touchdown," 
respectively. Cool & Dre, Irv Gotti, Nottz, J.R. Rotem, Scott Storch, DJ 
Toomp, Hi-Tek and Kanye West lend their production efforts to the album.
